NAME
    Acme::Futuristic::Perl - because Modern::Perl is too old

SYNOPSIS
            use Acme::Futuristic::Perl;

DESCRIPTION
    Sets the $] and $^V variables to 7.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs to
    <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=Acme-Futuristic-Perl>.

SEE ALSO
    perlvar.

